```plantuml
@startuml CMUChimpsLab_Peekaboo

actor User
participant NodeRED_UI
participant ProviderNode
participant InferenceNode
participant FilterNode
participant NetworkNode
participant PeekabooService
participant ExternalService

User -> NodeRED_UI: Drag & Drop Nodes
NodeRED_UI -> ProviderNode: Configure (Pull/Push)
NodeRED_UI -> InferenceNode: Configure (Model/Type)
NodeRED_UI -> FilterNode: Configure (Filter Type)
NodeRED_UI -> NetworkNode: Configure (Endpoint)

ProviderNode -> InferenceNode: Raw Data (msg.payload)
InferenceNode -> PeekabooService: Process Request
PeekabooService -> ExternalService: API Call
ExternalService --> PeekabooService: Inference Results
PeekabooService --> InferenceNode: Processed Data
InferenceNode -> FilterNode: Annotated Data

FilterNode -> NetworkNode: Filtered Data
NetworkNode -> ExternalService: HTTP Post
ExternalService --> NetworkNode: ACK

@enduml
```